00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.334
those kids in the back of the room
that are shouting, "Gotcha! Gotcha!

00:01:09.358 --> 00:01:11.976
Your eyebrow twitched.
You flared your nostril.

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.976
I watch that TV show 'Lie To Me.'
I know you're lying."

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:16.976
No, liespotters are armed

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.976
